    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 5. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The RH < 1 criterion provides a conservative regulatory margin. The assessment package is accepted for submission.",
